BillingInterface is a BusinessTask
    owned by bl

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            Reports
                BillingInterfaceReport
                BillingInterfaceListing

    Parameters
        Company                 is a BillingCompany
        CompanyGroup            is a GeneralLedgerCompanyGroup
        ProcessLevel            is a BillingProcessLevel
        CurrencyCd              is a Currency
        Description             is AlphaUpper size 30
        UpdateOption            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                EditOnly      value is "N"
                    default label is "Edit only"
                EditAndUpdate value is "Y"
                    default label is "Edit and update"
        ReleaseOption           is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                DoNotReleaseBatch            value is "N"
                    default label is "Do not release batch"
                ReleaseBatchToInvoicePrint   value is "Y"
                    default label is "Release batch to Invoice print"
                ReleaseAndBypassInvoicePrint value is "B"
                    default label is "Release and bypass Invoice print"
        ProcessComments         is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                NoCommentsToProcess    value is "N"
                    default label is "No Comments to process"
                CommentsExistToProcess value is "Y"
                    default label is "Comments Exist to process"
        ProcessAoc              is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                NoAocRecordsToProcess    value is "N"
                    default label is "No AOC records to process"
                AocRecordsExistToProcess value is "Y"
                    default label is "AOC records exist to process"
        CertNbrOption           is AlphaUpper size 1     
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"

    Parameter Rules
        CompanyGroup
            constraint (Company not entered)
            	"BothCompanyAndCompanyGroupCannotBeEntered"
        UpdateOption
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        ReleaseOption
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        ProcessComments
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        ProcessAoc
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        CertNbrOption
            initial value is "N"
            default to "N"

    Actions
        BillingInterface is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
